<\begin{Question_en}>
	(a) Briefly describe the motion of the object from $ t = 0 s $ to $ t = 4 s $ 
<\end{Question_en}>


<\begin{Question_zh}>
	
<\end{Question_zh}>

<\begin{Mark}>
	2
<\end{Mark}>


<\begin{Answer}>
	The object moves to left with a decelerating speed, it starts from $ 10ms^-1 $ to left at $ t = 0s $ to momentarily at rest at $ t = 4s $ 
<\end{Answer}>

